<view class="page-shell market-page">
  <view class="topbar">
    <view class="brand-row">
      <view class="brand-pin"></view>
      <text class="brand-text">兰州美食</text>
    </view>
    <view class="topbar-actions">
      <view class="icon-button">行</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <text class="eyebrow">EXPERIENCE</text>
    <text class="section-title">特色体验组合</text>
    <text class="market-intro">这里保留少量预约能力，但页面定位已经调整为“宣传延伸体验”入口，用于承接答辩展示中的特色套餐、线下路线与主题体验。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="market-tip section-block">
    <text class="market-tip-title">使用说明</text>
    <text class="market-tip-text">优先浏览专题内容与文化介绍；如需实际体验，再进入对应组合详情并完成手机号绑定后预约。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="market-feature card" wx:if="{{featuredProduct}}">
    <view bindtap="goToDetail" data-id="{{featuredProduct.foodId}}">
      <image src="{{featuredProduct.coverImage}}" class="market-feature-image" mode="aspectFill" />
      <view class="market-feature-body">
        <text class="pill pill-secondary">宣传延伸路线</text>
        <text class="market-feature-title">{{featuredProduct.name}}</text>
        <text class="market-copy">适合在答辩中作为“从宣传内容延伸到线下体验”的示例，不再以纯交易作为主叙事。</text>
        <view class="market-price-row">
          <text class="market-price">¥{{featuredProduct.groupPrice}}</text>
          <text class="market-origin">参考价 ¥{{featuredProduct.originalPrice}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="market-meta">{{featuredProduct.minPeople}}人成团 · 剩余名额 {{featuredProduct.stock}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="market-join" bindtap="quickOrder" data-index="0">前往预约</view>
  </view>

  <view class="market-grid">
    <view class="market-card card" wx:for="{{otherProducts}}" wx:key="_id">
      <view bindtap="goToDetail" data-id="{{item.foodId}}">
        <image src="{{item.coverImage}}" class="market-card-image" mode="aspectFill" />
        <view class="market-card-body">
          <text class="market-card-title">{{item.name}}</text>
          <text class="market-copy">查看这组美食主题体验对应的内容介绍与组合信息。</text>
          <view class="market-price-row">
            <text class="market-price">¥{{item.groupPrice}}</text>
            <text class="market-origin">参考价 ¥{{item.originalPrice}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="market-join" bindtap="quickOrder" data-index="{{index + 1}}">了解并预约</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
